TeCNO — temporal convolutional model for surgical phase recognition; uses frame sequences/features.

EndoNet-style models — CNN-based tool and phase recognition from laparoscopic video frames; can be extended with temporal smoothing or LSTM/TCN.

CNN + LSTM / CNN + TCN — standard temporal pipeline: frame feature extraction followed by sequence modeling.

TimeSformer / VideoMAE / SlowFast — general video action-recognition models that directly use frame sequences/video clips.